Sir Michael Caine was spotted out and about in London with his wife Shakira today. The Italian Job star, 89, was seen being supported by an assistant who gave him a helping hand as he walked with a frame. The legendary actor put on a dapper display in a pair of dark trousers, light blue shirt and jacket which he paired with a baseball cap. His wife of nearly 50 years, Shakira, was the epitome of glam in a long white shirt with a jumper tied around her waist. It after the star was spotted with Shakira leaving Langan's Brasserie in Mayfair in December.